Agnes Quaye (amụrụ n'ụbọchị nke ise, n'ọnwa Ọktoba n'afọ 1989) bụ onye Ghana na-agba bọọlụ nke na-agba dịka onye na-agba n'etiti bọọlụ maka otu egwuregwu bọọlụ ụmụ nwanyị nke mba Ghana
Ọ bụ otu n'ime ndị otu na 2014 African Women's Championship
Na klọb, ọ gbara bọọlụ maka Immigration Accra na Ghana.
